# TwoPaneView Demo

`TwoPaneView` control provides a split-view layout that can be sized using pixel values, proportional settings, or by adapting to a foldable device like Microsoft Surface Duo.

Example on Windows:

![Windows example of Uno.UI.Foldable TwoPaneView control](screenshot-TwoPaneViewDemo.png)

On Android, include the **Uno.UI.Foldable** NuGet in your project to add the foldable-detection behavior, otherwise it will layout according to the pixel/proportional settings in code.